As a logged in user, you are able to access the movie searching feature, where you can look up your favorite movies. Using the search bar, which you can access from the homepage, you can search up the name of any movie. This will give you back a list of the top movies that match your search. You have to option of adding your already known favorite movies to your favorite movie list, which you can access on your profile page, or you can learn more about the movie, leading you to the trailer for that movie, giving you the option to choose whether this movie deserves to be in your favorites.